title: Esquire's Sexiest Woman Alive is the sultry Emilia Clarke
text:
> Entertainment Esquire's Sexiest Woman Alive is the sultry Emilia Clarke FILE - In this Jan. 12, 2014 file photo, actress Emilia Clarke arrives at the 71st annual Golden Globe Awards in Beverly Hills, Calif. The 28-year-old Clarke, who plays menacing, white-haired Daenerys Targaryen, aka Khaleesi, aka Mother of Dragons on "Game of Thrones," is Esquire's Sexiest Woman Alive. The magazine made the announcement early Tuesday, Oct. 13. (Photo by Jordan Strauss/Invision/AP, File)
